                   "AI Image"
            ],
            "date_published": "2026-07-19T01:01:24-04:00",
            "date_modified": "2026-07-19T01:01:24-04:00"
        },
        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/forest-creatures.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/forest-creatures.html",
            "title": "Forest Creatures",
            "summary": "This is one of my exercise pages, I draw a fun landscape&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"3\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/34/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00739_.png\" data-size=\"1104x1480\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/34/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00739_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1030\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/34/gallery/scan0004.jpg\" data-size=\"1578x2119\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/34/gallery/scan0004-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1031\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/34/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00737_.png\" data-size=\"1104x1480\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/34/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00737_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1030\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/34/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00736_.png\" data-size=\"1104x1480\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/34/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00736_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1030\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/34/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00735_.png\" data-size=\"1104x1480\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/34/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00735_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1030\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/34/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00734_.png\" data-size=\"1104x1480\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/34/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00734_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1030\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/34/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00733_.png\" data-size=\"1104x1480\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/34/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00733_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1030\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/34/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00732_.png\" data-size=\"1104x1480\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/34/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00732_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1030\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/34/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00731_.png\" data-size=\"1104x1480\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/34/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00731_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1030\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>This is one of my exercise pages, I draw a fun landscape to stretch the mind as a warm up, and in an effort to mix things up, I added character with a touch of whimsy and to explore a look blacked in a section with marker . For the AI image I was curious of it's interpretation of the contrast in mediums, and gave it a few different prompts to see how it changed it's method of style.</p>",
            "image": "https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/34/Qwen_Edit_2511_00733_.png",
            "author": {
                "name": "Rudy"
            },
