                   "Sketch",
                   "Rough Sketch",
                   "AI Image"
            ],
            "date_published": "2026-07-19T00:44:04-04:00",
            "date_modified": "2026-07-19T00:45:42-04:00"
        },
        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/baby-boomer.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/baby-boomer.html",
            "title": "Baby Boomer",
            "summary": "This was a project from when I went back to school for&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"3\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/33/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00647_.png\" data-size=\"1536x1312\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/33/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00647_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"656\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/33/gallery/baby-boomer.jpg\" data-size=\"2086x1782\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/33/gallery/baby-boomer-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"656\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/33/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00648_.png\" data-size=\"1536x1312\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/33/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00648_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"656\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/33/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00646_.png\" data-size=\"1536x1312\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/33/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00646_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"656\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/33/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00645_.png\" data-size=\"1536x1312\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/33/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00645_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"656\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/33/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00641_.png\" data-size=\"1536x1312\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/33/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00641_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"656\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/33/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00640_.png\" data-size=\"1536x1312\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/33/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00640_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"656\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/33/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00638_.png\" data-size=\"1536x1312\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/33/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00638_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"656\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/33/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00637_.png\" data-size=\"1536x1312\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/33/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00637_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"656\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>This was a project from when I went back to school for interactive media and design. The concept for this colored pencil drawing was meant to show the meeting of life and death, using iconic symbology to create a thought stimulating scene. Some elements of the scene where added to allow the mind to run free and allow the viewer to question the thoughts in their mind of what they are seeing.</p>",
            "image": "https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/33/Qwen_Edit_2511_00638_.png",
            "author": {
                "name": "Rudy"
            },
            "tags": [
                   "Sketch",
                   "Colored Pencil",
                   "AI Image"
            ],
            "date_published": "2026-07-18T21:56:09-04:00",
            "date_modified": "2026-07-18T21:56:58-04:00"
        },
        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/all-things-are-connected.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/all-things-are-connected.html",
            "title": "All Things are Connected",
            "summary": "The concept for this sketch was to show the unseen connection between&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"3\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/32/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00428_.png\" data-size=\"1192x1240\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/32/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00428_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"799\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/32/gallery/20241108_201720.jpg\" data-size=\"1195x1240\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/32/gallery/20241108_201720-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"797\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/32/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00427_.png\" data-size=\"1192x1240\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/32/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00427_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"799\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/32/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00408_.png\" data-size=\"1192x1240\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/32/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00408_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"799\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/32/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00164_.png\" data-size=\"1024x1024\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/32/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00164_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"768\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>The concept for this sketch was to show the unseen connection between all planes of existence. Each shares a part with everything in the universe of matter and beyond. The woman in the foreground represents the unseen, the background was one of my living spaces many decades ago. This was extremely challenging to try and get AI to create a cohesive image in just one go.</p>",
            "image": "https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/32/Qwen_Edit_2511_00429_.png",
            "author": {
                "name": "Rudy"
            },
            "tags": [
                   "Sketch",
                   "Rough Sketch",
                   "AI Image"
            ],
            "date_published": "2026-07-18T21:08:39-04:00",
            "date_modified": "2026-07-18T21:08:39-04:00"
        },
        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/angelic-love.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/angelic-love.html",
            "title": "Angelic Love",
            "summary": "I created this sketch while I was out of state painting the&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"3\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/31/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00488_.png\" data-size=\"1160x1536\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/31/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00488_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1017\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/31/gallery/scan0002.jpg\" data-size=\"1660x2201\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/31/gallery/scan0002-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1018\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/31/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00487_.png\" data-size=\"1160x1536\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/31/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00487_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1017\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/31/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00486_.png\" data-size=\"1160x1536\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/31/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00486_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1017\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/31/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00485_.png\" data-size=\"1160x1536\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/31/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00485_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1017\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/31/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00484_.png\" data-size=\"1160x1536\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/31/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00484_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1017\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/31/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00483_.png\" data-size=\"1160x1536\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/31/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00483_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1017\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/31/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00482_.png\" data-size=\"1160x1536\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/31/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00482_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1017\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>I created this sketch while I was out of state painting the backside of a Lowes for a contract paint company. The men I drove to the job wanted to go to a gentleman's club after we were done with the job and one of the dancer's inspired me to draw this. The AI version is the complete scene of what I saw which was her soul, and the background represents the place we both where in. Even in the darkest of places beauty can shine bright : ) </p>",
            "image": "https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/31/Qwen_Edit_2511_00486_.png",
            "author": {
                "name": "Rudy"
            },
            "tags": [
                   "Rough Sketch",
                   "Characters",
                   "AI Image"
            ],
            "date_published": "2026-07-18T20:30:28-04:00",
            "date_modified": "2026-07-18T20:40:03-04:00"
        },
        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/imagine-you-are-a-day.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/imagine-you-are-a-day.html",
            "title": "Imagine you are a Day",
            "summary": "This was a poem I made for my mother when she was&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"3\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/30/gallery/100_1273.JPG\" data-size=\"1932x2576\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/30/gallery/100_1273-thumbnail.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/30/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01779_.png\" data-size=\"1544x1152\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/30/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01779_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"573\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/30/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01763_.png\" data-size=\"1472x1104\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/30/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01763_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"576\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/30/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01756_.png\" data-size=\"1472x1104\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/30/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01756_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"576\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/30/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01750_.png\" data-size=\"1472x1104\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/30/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01750_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"576\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/30/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01736_.png\" data-size=\"1328x1328\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/30/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01736_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"768\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/30/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01734_.png\" data-size=\"1544x1152\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/30/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01734_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"573\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>This was a poem I made for my mother when she was sick, I had her send me an image years later because so much time had passed I forgot what I wrote. I used AI to see how well it would keep the text it could see and make an interesting image to go with the poem. Imagine we found messages like this as we explore the universe.</p>",
            "image": "https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/30/Qwen_Edit_2511_01781_.png",
            "author": {
                "name": "Rudy"
            },
            "tags": [
                   "Sketch",
                   "Poem",
                   "AI Image"
            ],
            "date_published": "2026-07-17T20:08:49-04:00",
            "date_modified": "2026-07-17T20:09:13-04:00"
        },
        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/he-is-a-fungi.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/he-is-a-fungi.html",
            "title": "He is a fungi : )",
            "summary": "He is a fungi, a mushroom man standing outside his home. I&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"3\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/scan0081.jpg\" data-size=\"1579x2113\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/scan0081-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1028\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01853_.png\" data-size=\"1088x1496\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01853_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1056\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01850_.png\" data-size=\"1088x1496\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01850_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1056\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01839_.png\" data-size=\"1088x1496\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01839_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1056\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01838_.png\" data-size=\"1088x1496\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01838_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1056\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01833_.png\" data-size=\"1088x1496\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01833_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1056\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01831_.png\" data-size=\"1088x1496\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01831_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1056\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01829_.png\" data-size=\"1088x1496\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01829_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1056\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01828_.png\" data-size=\"1088x1496\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01828_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1056\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>He is a fungi, a mushroom man standing outside his home. I was exploring different methods of creating an image by changing the math used to form the image during the process an AI goes thru in a comfyui environment, using a starting image which was one of my old drawings.</p>",
